ent = new TestComponent();\n\n            TestFacesListener[] listeners = component.facesListeners(TestFacesListener.class);\n\n            assertThat(context).isSameAs(FacesContext.getCurrentInstance());\n            assertThat(listeners).isEmpty();\n            assertThat(listeners.getClass().getComponentType()).isEqualTo(TestFacesListener.class);\n        }\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void getFacesListenersReturnsTypedEmptyArrayAfterAllListenersAreRemoved() {\n        try (TestFacesContext context = TestFacesContext.activate()) {\n            TestComponent component = new TestComponent();\n            TestFacesListener listener = new TestFacesListener();\n            component.addListener(listener);\n\n            component.removeListener(listener);\n            TestFacesListener[] listeners = component.facesListeners(TestFacesListener.class);\n\n            assertThat(context).isSameAs(FacesContext.getCurrentInstance());\n            assertThat(listeners).isEmpty();\n            assertThat(listeners.getClass().getComponentType()).isEqualTo(TestFacesListener.class);\n        }\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void getFacesListenersReturnsMatchingListenersInTypedArray() {\n        try (TestFacesContext context = TestFacesContext.activate()) {\n            TestComponent component = new TestComponent();\n            TestFacesListener listener = new TestFacesListener();\n            component.addListener(listener);\n            component.addListener(new OtherFacesListener());\n\n            TestFacesListener[] listeners = component.facesListeners(TestFacesListener.class);\n\n            assertThat(context).isSameAs(FacesContext.getCurrentInstance());\n            assertThat(listeners).containsExactly(listener);\n            assertThat(listeners.getClass().getComponentType()).isEqualTo(TestFacesListener.class);\n        }\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void restoreAttachedCollectionStateInstantiatesOriginalCollectionType() {\n        try (TestFacesContext context = TestFacesContext.activate()) {\n            ArrayList<String> attachedState = new ArrayList<>();\n            attachedState.add(\"first\");\n            attachedState.add(\"second\");\n\n            Object savedState = UIComponentBase.saveAttachedState(context, attachedState);\n            Object restoredState = UIComponentBase.restoreAttachedState(context, savedState);\n\n            assertThat(restoredState).isInstanceOf(ArrayList.class);\n            assertThat(restoredState).isEqualTo(attachedState);\n        }\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void restoreAttachedMapStateInstantiatesOriginalMapType() {\n        try (TestFacesContext context = TestFacesContext.activate()) {\n            LinkedHashMap<String, String> attachedState = new LinkedHashMap<>();\n            attachedState.put(\"first\", \"one\");\n            attachedState.put(\"second\", \"two\");\n\n            Object savedState = UIComponentBase.saveAttachedState(context, attachedState);\n            Object restoredState = UIComponentBase.restoreAttachedState(context, savedState);\n\n            assertThat(restoredState).isInstanceOf(LinkedHashMap.class);\n            assertThat(restoredState).isEqualTo(attachedState);\n        }\n    }\n\n    public static class TestComponent extends UIComponentBase {\n        @Override\n        public String getFamily() {\n            return \"test\";\n        }\n\n        void addListener(FacesListener listener) {\n            addFacesListener(listener);\n        }\n\n        void removeListener(FacesListener listener) {\n            removeFacesListener(listener);\n        }\n\n        @SuppressWarnings(\"unchecked\")\n        <T extends FacesListener> T[] facesListeners(Class<T> listenerType) {\n            return (T[]) getFacesListeners(listenerType);\n        }\n    }\n\n    public static class TestFacesListener implements FacesListener {\n    }\n\n    public static class OtherFacesListener implements FacesListener {\n    }\n\n    private static final class TestFacesContext extends FacesContext implements AutoCloseable {\n        static TestFacesContext activate() {\n            TestFacesContext context = new TestFacesContext();\n            setCurrentInstance(context);\n            return context;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public Application getApplication() {\n            return null;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public Iterator<String> getClientIdsWithMessages() {\n            return Collections.emptyIterator();\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public Lifecycle getLifecycle() {\n            return null;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public ExternalContext getExternalContext() {\n            return null;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public Severity getMaximumSeverity() {\n            return null;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public Iterator<FacesMessage> getMessages() {\n            return Collections.emptyIterator();\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public Iterator<FacesMessage> getMessages(String clientId) {\n            return Collections.emptyIterator();\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public RenderKit getRenderKit() {\n            return null;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public boolean getRenderResponse() {\n            return false;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public boolean getResponseComplete() {\n            return false;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public ResponseStream getResponseStream() {\n            return null;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public void setResponseStream(ResponseStream responseStream) {\n            throw new UnsupportedOperationException(\"Response streams are not used by this test\");\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public ResponseWriter getResponseWriter() {\n            return null;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public void setResponseWriter(ResponseWriter responseWriter) {\n            throw new UnsupportedOperationException(\"Response writers are not used by this test\");\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public UIViewRoot getViewRoot() {\n            return null;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public void setViewRoot(UIViewRoot root) {\n            throw new UnsupportedOperationException(\"View roots are not used by this test\");\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public void addMessage(String clientId, FacesMessage message) {\n            throw new UnsupportedOperationException(\"Faces messages are not used by this test\");\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public void release() {\n            setCurrentInstance(null);\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public void renderResponse() {\n            throw new UnsupportedOperationException(\"Rendering is not used by this test\");\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public void responseComplete() {\n            throw new UnsupportedOperationException(\"Response completion is not used by this test\");\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public void close() {\n            release();\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1778513067878}]}
